meta.v1.2_changes: Expert f26r analysis: dy lock-end->close (C597), ee cool->deep-equilibrate (C901), ecth null->settle-cut (compound e+cth)

meta.frame_transfer_taxonomy: Frame/transfer taxonomy: al 'transfer'->'collect' (differentiated from t 'transfer' via suffix patterns: al=93% bare/self-terminating, t=always suffixed/active process). Compounds updated: alo, alsh, ald, alch, opal, edal, eal (2026-02-06)
meta.gloss_honesty_overhaul: v2.0: Nulled 7 speculative glosses then re-derived from behavioral data. h 'hazard'->'monitor' (C104 finger test). FL state markers (i,r,l,o,m) relabeled to stage:early/mid/late/near-end/final. d->'checkpoint', f->'flag'.
